   :topic: Lists/Exercises
   :from_source: T
   :nocodelens:

   Here are the rules for an L-system that creates something that resembles
   a common garden herb.  Implement the following rules and try it.  Use an
   angle of 25.7 degrees.

   ::

       H
       H --> HFX[+H][-H]
       X --> X[-FFF][+FFF]FX
   ~~~~